description:
This is a 29 minute workout called 'Chair Yoga Stretch for Beginners, Seniors & Everyone || 30 minutes' from the channel SeniorShape Fitness.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Unwind, stretch and feel amazing with this great yoga workout all done in the comfort of a chair at home. 

This video is easy to follow and is perfect for all fitness levels.  In 30 minutes you will decrease stress and relieve sore and achy muscles and joints.

As always, please go at a pace you are comfortable with and don’t push yourself. Remember to breathe (even though I’ll tell you 100 times)!

Here is the link to the great yoga shoes that I’m wearing. They are perfect for any type of mat class. They are supportive and keep your feet from slipping. Please enter “SeniorShape” at checkout so they know I sent you.
https://barreletics.com/
